ğŸ“Œ The 7 RESTful Routes
HTTP Verb	Path	Controller#Action	Purpose
GET	/users	users#index	List all users
GET	/users/new	users#new	Form to create user
POST	/users	users#create	Create user
GET	/users/:id	users#show	Show user
GET	/users/:id/edit	users#edit	Edit user form
PATCH / PUT	/users/:id	users#update	Update user
DELETE	/users/:id	users#destroy	Delete user
ğŸ§  Why exactly 7?

Rails follows REST conventions:

Collection actions â†’ index, create

Member actions â†’ show, update, destroy

Form helpers â†’ new, edit

